---
title: State Machine — Election3.sol Phase Transitions
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Created : Contract deployed
    
    state Created {
        [*] --> setMerkleRoot
        [*] --> setIdentityMerkleRoot
        [*] --> setRegCodeMerkleRoot
    }
    
    Created --> Registration : startRegistration(end)
    
    state Registration {
        [*] --> registerCandidate
        [*] --> setMerkleRoot
        [*] --> setIdentityMerkleRoot
        [*] --> setRegCodeMerkleRoot
        [*] --> verifyRegCode
    }
    
    Registration --> Voting : startVoting(end)
    
    state Voting {
        [*] --> castVote
        [*] --> vote
        [*] --> getCandidate
    }
    
    Voting --> Ended : endElection()
    
    state Ended {
        [*] --> startNewElection
        [*] --> getElectionResult
        [*] --> getHistoricalCandidate
    }
    
    Ended --> Created : startNewElection()
    
    note right of Registration
        Merkle roots can be updated in
        Created and Registration phases.
        Frozen once Voting begins.
    end note
    
    note right of Voting
        Merkle proof is required.
        At least 2 female GM votes
        enforced in castVote.
    end note
    
    note right of Ended
        Winner algorithm in startNewElection:
        President & Secretary: highest votes.
        GM: 2-pass (2 female, then 3 any).
    end note
